<H3> <TI>   DPRK Reportedly Rejects Nuclear Inspections </TI></H3>
<H4>   `Total Rejection' of Inspections </H4>
<F P=102> SK0302025094 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network in Korean 0230 GMT 3 
Feb 94 </F>

