<DOCNO> FBIS3-28273 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas024__a94007" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-024-A </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  4 February 1994 </DATE1>

