price rate 
increase % 

Scenario B     Separated from standard forecast values 

7.5 trillion   -7.5     -7.5      -7.5      -7.5     -7.5      -7.5      -7.5 
yen 
individual 
income tax 
cut 

6%             0.00     3.0       3.0       3.0      3.0       3.0       3.0 
consumption 
