10 trillion    -10      -10       -10       -10      -10       -10       -10 
yen 
individual 
income tax 
cut 

7%             0.00     4.0       4.0       4.0      4.0       4.0       4.0 
consumption 
tax rate 

Consumption    0.00     9.7       10.3      10.9     11.6      12.3      13.3 
tax revenue 
increase 
(trillion 
yen) 

